{"tid":2109343,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"上車客疫市下「無樓睇」以555萬元購荃景花園2房","createTime":"2020-07-15T07:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T10:55:30.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"58162856a921ea983f22cd7a9b85104110629698","tid":2109343,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:43:47.000Z","msg":"上車客疫市下「無樓睇」以555萬元購荃景花園2房<br />\n文章日期：2020年7月15日 14:25<br />\n<br />\n&quot;....上述單位為荃景花園6座中層E室，實用面積362方呎，屬2房間隔﹐原業主最初開價560萬元放盤，惟自本地疫情急轉惡化下，不願意開門予準買家睇樓，即使有準買家願意支付500元作清潔費亦遭拒絕開門。而新買家為上車客，最終在「無樓睇」及議價後，以555萬元購入單位，實呎15331元。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1594794485991&amp;issue=20200715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1594794485991%26issue%3D20200715&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=cc007396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1594794485991&amp;issue=20200715</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">「無樓睇」都照買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"93f204266b87dcc6ec8c6dc55267823c9a71be60","tid":2109343,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:45:13.000Z","msg":"香港人 錢多"},{"pid":"23e0fe1cc8ef1be9d83b9eafd272860e241f5997","tid":2109343,"uid":265485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:56:16.000Z","msg":"比500幻買一件未睇過嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ad845d4389b2bc1c0e5703e2f1c643a11a7f8b","tid":2109343,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23e0fe1cc8ef1be9d83b9eafd272860e241f5997","tid":2109343,"uid":265485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:56:16.000Z","msg":"比500幻買一件未睇過嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"